7865.htm target="_blank"><img src=xin_20301090510401091268036.jpg width="136" height="88"></a></li><li><div class="textbg"></div>  <div class="text"><a href=http://news.xinhuanet.com/foto/2012-01/04/c_122534192.htm target="_blank">油画般的世界</a></div>  <a href=http://news.xinhuanet.com/foto/2012-01/04/c_122534192.htm target="_blank"><img src=xin_5130109041654203250235.jpg width="136" height="88"></a></li></div>
